    <div class="body">
      &quot;bitcoins get harder to mine over time.&quot;<br /><br />This is not true. The difficulty dynamically adjusts in both directions depending on if more mining power comes online or goes offline. From Dec '12 to Feb '13 the difficulty decreased.
      
