ons because this company can´t deliver next month or next year. So good luck with that ROI.<br /><br />Lets assume you invest 10,000$ in mining gear and make all the ROI and hardware, and mining calculations you want, in order to do this, you need to know when your manufacturer is going to ship and when are you going to start to produce. Lets not forget every XX time the difficulty of the network increases.<br /><br />And this math is something you cant. They say 2 months in their website or more, so lets assume you are optimistic and make a 5 months calculation. But in reality this company has not shipped a single, A SINGLE one of the orders sold this year. They are still not not catching up with orders from July of last year. This are not 2 months we are speaking here, we are speaking of more than one year and no where near this pre-orders are going to be fulfilled this years. Rumors say that orders from this years will be delivered in 2014, half of 2014.<br /><br />So good luck with all your calculations. RIGHT NOW in the forums people already made the math and their cheapest device the Jalapeno, does not produce income as we write this. Today, if you received it today you would not make the ROI back ever, assuming you actually get it this year.<br /><br />So think of it as a hobby, because all you will end up is with a cheap device that generates noise and power, consumes power and is probably going to die after a couple of months of use. There are some pictures of ones that actually burned. So don´t expect this devices which are very cheap crap to last forever. There is no way anyone is going to make any ROI back once they get this units.
      
