      <div class="quotetitle"><a href="http://arstechnica.com/civis/viewtopic.php?p=25255501#p25255501" class="postlink" rel="nofollow">kentadams</a> wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I still don't get the whole bitcoin thing.</div><br /><br />I see Bitcoins as more suitable for micro-transactions. As a get-rich-quick scheme, not so much.
      
